es Tacchella]]\n|-\n|''[[Let Joy Reign Supreme]]''||''Que la f\u00eate commence''||[[Bertrand Tavernier]]\n|-\n|''[[Sept morts sur ordonnance|Seven Deaths by Prescription]]''||''Sept morts sur ordonnance''||[[Jacques Rouffio]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[2nd C\u00e9sar Awards|1977]]||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"|''[[Monsieur Klein|Mr. Klein]]''||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"|''Monsieur Klein''||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"|[[Joseph Losey]]\n|-\n|colspan=\"2\"|''[[Barocco]]''||[[Andr\u00e9 T\u00e9chin\u00e9]]\n|-\n|''[[La Meilleure fa\u00e7on de marcher|The Best Way to Walk]]''||''La Meilleure Fa\u00e7on de marcher''||[[Claude Miller]]\n|-\n|''[[The Judge and the Assassin]]''||''Le Juge et l'assassin''||[[Bertrand Tavernier]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[3rd C\u00e9sar Awards|1978]]||colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"|''[[Providence (1977 film)|Providence]]''||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"|[[Alain Resnais]]\n|-\n|''[[Le Crabe-tambour|Drummer-Crab]]''||''Le Crabe-Tambour''||[[Pierre Schoendoerffer]]\n|-\n|''[[The Lacemaker]]''||''La Dentelli\u00e8re''||[[Claude Goretta]]\n|-\n|''[[Nous irons tous au paradis|We Will All Meet in Paradise]]''||''Nous irons tous au paradis''||[[Yves Robert]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[4th C\u00e9sar Awards|1979]]||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"|''[[L'Argent des autres|Other People's Money]]''||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"|''L'Argent des autres''||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"|[[Christian de Chalonge]]\n|-\n|''[[Le dossier 51|Dossier 51]]''||''Le Dossier 51''||[[Michel Deville]]\n|-\n|colspan=\"2\"|''[[Moli\u00e8re (1978 film)|Moli\u00e8re]]''||[[Ariane Mnouchkine]]\n|-\n|''[[A Simple Story (1978 film)|A Simple Story]]''||''Une histoire simple''||[[Claude Sautet]]\n|-\n|}\n\n===1980s===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!width=\"100\"|'''Year'''\n!width=\"300\"|'''English title'''\n!width=\"300\"|'''Original title'''\n!width=\"300\"|'''Director'''\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\